{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"484ba8c871","title":"致《新山大》编辑部的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9db628fbf7","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":24,"articleId":"484ba8c871"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"413c49cc72","name":"沈汉祥"},{"id":"7f59b6c7ba","name":"山东大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9e85d4a95a","type":"title","text":"致《新山大》编辑部的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"484ba8c871"},{"id":"d42e3500ad","type":"authors","text":"山东大学沈汉祥","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"484ba8c871"},{"id":"cb0e80699c","type":"subtitle","text":"(沈汉祥：山东大学水产系教授)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"484ba8c871"},{"id":"1d0bf084fd","type":"appellation","text":"《新山大》270期“民盟山大支部讨论党委制”一文，关于我的发言记录中，没有将要点表达出来。我原来的发言要点是：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"484ba8c871"},{"id":"c4f0197f1f","type":"paragraph","text":"“校长负责制，不要党委领导下的校长负责制，以免校长不是党员时，校长反被党委书记所领导的‘校长有职无权’等现象。重要问题应由校委会讨论，决定后作为校长的参考。校委会仍为校长的咨询机构。校委会包括党委会的人员在内。党的意图，可建议给校委会，党可在校委会中起领导作用。倘校委会的决议，校长老是不采纳的话，校委会可向高教部反映，而党委也可向高教部反映意见。这样可以纠正校长的偏差。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"484ba8c871"},{"id":"5fd904bc97","type":"paragraph","text":" 沈汉祥 1957年6月24日","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"484ba8c871"},{"id":"f15b33cd5f","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：1957年7月5日《新山大》。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"484ba8c871"}],"page":{"id":"e9bbf92130","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"484ba8c871","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}